Class LinkedStructure<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • structures.commons.LinkedStructure<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - Generic type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<E>, DataStructure<E>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LinkedList, LinkedQueue, LinkedStack

    public abstract class LinkedStructure<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataStructure<E>, java.lang.Iterable<E>
    Abstract class that all linked structures such as linked lists, linked queues, etc will extend.
